                {
                  "id": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3db7w98g/manifest/annotation/p3",
                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>as much a <hi rend=\"underline\"><persName>Pollock</persName></hi> as any of them.<lb/>\n                <add>כל המחובר וגו'</add>.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I gave <persName>Sarah Joseph</persName> your<lb/> message, and she\n                wishes I believe to<lb/> make an enclosure for you in this.<lb/> If she is “up to\n                time”, well, if not, you<lb/> will get it another time.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I heard lately that <persName>Mr<lb/> Dd Judah</persName> of\n                    <placeName>Baltimore</placeName> has gone the way<lb/> of all the earth. He was\n                    <hi rend=\"underline\">nominally</hi><lb/> my agent for that city, and when\n                he<lb/> died, held some books or proceeds thereof<lb/> on hand. Would you kindly\n                inform me<lb/> as to the best means of proceeding to<lb/> obtain one or the\n                other?</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">With best wishes, and hoping<lb/> to hear soon from you</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(7)\">I remain yours faithfully</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(8)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">Abraham de Sola</persName>\n            </p>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3db7w98g/canvas/p3"
                }
              ]
            }
